Wow i made 2 surf maps in one day :D. Well this is a fun one as you can blow up the spawn if there are any AFK's, you can also get quite a bit of speed if you know how ;).

At the end of the map there is a hidden tube where you can go fly yes fly to spawn (its more of a push than flying).

As always have fun :D
